<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٥١:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: <span class="c3">{إِنَّ اللَّهَ يُحِبُّ الَّذِينَ يُقَاتِلُونَ فِي سَبِيلِهِ صَفًّا كَأَنَّهُمْ بُنْيَانٌ مَرْصُوصٌ}</span> <span class="c4">[الصف: ٤]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ ابْنُ عَبَّاسٍ:</span> <span class="c3">{مَرْصُوصٌ}</span>: <span class="c2">«مُلْصَقٌ بَعْضُهُ بِبَعْضٍ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ يَحْيَى:</span> <span class="c2">«بِالرَّصَاصِ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>